# Experimental!
# Fib mod n
Fp ← |2 memo(⨬(˜◿+∩⌟Fp⊃-₁-₂⊙(⟜∘)|⋅⋅1)⊸<₂)

PPer ← memo(
  ≡Fp⇡⊸×₂₀ # Take 20 terms.
  ≡↻⇡⊸⧻↯⊸⧻ # Look for first repeat of pattern...
  ≡↙¤⌊÷2⊸⧻
  /-↙2⊚≡≍¤°⊂
)
PisanoPrime ← ×PPer⟜˜ⁿ⊙-₁
Lcm         ← ÷⊃∨×
Pisano      ← ⨬(/Lcm⊕(PisanoPrime⊃⊢⧻)⊸⊛°/×|1)⊸=₁
≡⌟PisanoPrime [2 3 5 7 11 13] 2 # Part 1
≡⌟PisanoPrime⊙1▽⊸=⊣⊸°/×↘2⇡180   # Part 2
≡Pisano↘1⇡180                   # Part 3
